main event: A witness observed a round, luminous object moving rapidly upward out of sight in Compton, California.
interesting points: The witness observed the object for approximately 15 minutes.,The object was about the size of a dime at arm's length.,The observation was strictly visual with no physical evidence or photographs.,The object's course was upward during the sighting., The event took place on 22 September 2023.
witness description: the witness saw only one object moving rapidly
